{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":763,"text":"Organic chemists make molecules,"},{"time":3378,"text":"very complicated molecules,"},{"time":5194,"text":"by chopping up a big molecule into small molecules"},{"time":8878,"text":"and reverse engineering."},{"time":10739,"text":"And as a chemist,"},{"time":11778,"text":"one of the things I wanted to ask my research group a couple of years ago is,"},{"time":15245,"text":"could we make a really cool universal chemistry set?"},{"time":19396,"text":"In essence, could we \"app\" chemistry?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":24429,"text":"Now what would this mean, and how would we do it?"},{"time":27612,"text":"Well to start to do this,"},{"time":29583,"text":"we took a 3D printer"},{"time":31315,"text":"and we started to print our beakers and our test tubes on one side"},{"time":35617,"text":"and then print the molecule at the same time on the other side"},{"time":39682,"text":"and combine them together in what we call reactionware."},{"time":42836,"text":"And so by printing the vessel and doing the chemistry at the same time,"},{"time":47270,"text":"we may start to access this universal toolkit of chemistry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52437,"text":"Now what could this mean?"},{"time":53985,"text":"Well if we can embed biological and chemical networks like a search engine,"},{"time":59253,"text":"so if you have a cell that's ill that you need to cure"},{"time":62402,"text":"or bacteria that you want to kill,"},{"time":64121,"text":"if you have this embedded in your device"},{"time":66452,"text":"at the same time, and you do the chemistry,"},{"time":68901,"text":"you may be able to make drugs in a new way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72502,"text":"So how are we doing this in the lab?"},{"time":74902,"text":"Well it requires software, it requires hardware"},{"time":78001,"text":"and it requires chemical inks."},{"time":80367,"text":"And so the really cool bit is,"},{"time":81820,"text":"the idea is that we want to have a universal set of inks"},{"time":84867,"text":"that we put out with the printer,"},{"time":87136,"text":"and you download the blueprint, the organic chemistry for that molecule"},{"time":91418,"text":"and you make it in the device."},{"time":94418,"text":"And so you can make your molecule in the printer using this software."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99985,"text":"So what could this mean?"},{"time":102184,"text":"Well, ultimately, it could mean that you could print your own medicine."},{"time":107131,"text":"And this is what we're doing in the lab at the moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109100,"text":"But to take baby steps to get there,"},{"time":111002,"text":"first of all we want to look at drug design and production,"},{"time":113835,"text":"or drug discovery and manufacturing."},{"time":116485,"text":"Because if we can manufacture it after we've discovered it,"},{"time":119484,"text":"we could deploy it anywhere."},{"time":121618,"text":"You don't need to go to the chemist anymore."},{"time":123734,"text":"We can print drugs at point of need."},{"time":126102,"text":"We can download new diagnostics."},{"time":128757,"text":"Say a new super bug has emerged."},{"time":130768,"text":"You put it in your search engine,"},{"time":132385,"text":"and you create the drug to treat the threat."},{"time":135518,"text":"So this allows you on-the-fly molecular assembly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139206,"text":"But perhaps for me the core bit going into the future"},{"time":142201,"text":"is this idea of taking your own stem cells,"},{"time":145551,"text":"with your genes and your environment,"},{"time":147318,"text":"and you print your own personal medicine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150767,"text":"And if that doesn't seem fanciful enough,"},{"time":153019,"text":"where do you think we're going to go?"},{"time":155067,"text":"Well, you're going to have your own personal matter fabricator."},{"time":159651,"text":"Beam me up, Scotty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161551,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}